  "name": "Release Notes 3.14.1 - POS and Back Office",
  "body": "<p>This release will be available to all users between 6th - 15th October 2021</p>\n<h2 data-id=\"new-features\">New Features</h2>\n<h3 data-id=\"supplier-returns-are-here\">Supplier Returns are here</h3>\n<p>We're excited to announce the release of Supplier Returns, an exciting new addition to Retail Express.</p>\n<p>Returning goods and claiming credits from your Suppliers is a key function for many retailers and we are excited to offer you a new tool to effectively manage this process.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Supplier Returns.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWhEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>Supplier Returns allows you to manage claims to your Suppliers, for example:</p>\n<ul><li>Faulty/damaged products</li><li>Short shipped</li><li>Overcharged</li><li>Sale or Return arrangements</li></ul><p><span>As Suppliers may make decisions about your claims at different times, you can apply multiple Credit Notes against a single Supplier Return, or cancel items if a Supplier rejects the claim. </span></p>\n<p>Find out more - <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Announcing-Supplier-Returns\">click here to read the announcement</a></p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Important: </strong>MYOB Manual Accounting Export integration users will need to <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/MYOB-Accounting-Data-Export-Setup\">download new setup files</a> before using Supplier Returns (due to the new Purchase Variance account - 59999). </p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<h3 data-id=\"myob-cloud-integration\">MYOB Cloud Integration</h3>\n<p>We're excited to announce we've expanded our Accounting Integration options, with a new MYOB Cloud Integration! </p>\n<p>Streamline your accounting processes and get accurate financial insights to make better business decisions.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"accounting integration.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWmEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>Compatible with MYOB AccountRight19+ (where the Company File is stored online), this integration offers a daily automated synchronisation of data from Retail Express to create transactions within MYOB.</p>\n<p>Find out more - <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Announcing-the-new-MYOB-Cloud-Integration\">click here to read the announcement</a>. </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<h3 data-id=\"receipts-and-invoices-display-card-digits\">Receipts and Invoices display card digits</h3>\n<p>Receipts and Invoices paid using Fiserv, Linkly or PC-EFTPOS (both Australia and New Zealand) integrations now display the last 4 digits of the card used to pay!</p>\n<div>\n<p>Please note: this feature is not available for payments made via Tyro or non-integrated Payment Types</p>\n</div>\n<p>To display the last 4 digits of the card, you will need to enable the \"Show Payment History\" option in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Invoice-and-Receipt-Settings\">Invoice and Receipt Settings</a>.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"improvements\">Improvements</h2>\n<h3 data-id=\"purchase-order-total-order-quantity\">Purchase Order Total Order Quantity</h3>\n<p>We've added the \"Total Order Quantity\" to Purchase Orders, both when creating a PO and on the PO Templates printed and provided to the supplier.</p>\n<div><br/><div><br/><div><img alt=\"mceclip3 (40).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeSbEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><div><img alt=\"mceclip4 (28).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWrEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></div><br/></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<h3 data-id=\"purchase-order-supplier-sku-and-original-departure-date\">Purchase Order Supplier SKU and Original Departure Date</h3>\n<p>You can now customise your Purchase Orders, optionally displaying the following:</p>\n<ul><li>Whether to show the Supplier SKU and/or Supplier SKU2</li><li>The Original Date of Departure</li></ul><p><img alt=\"mceclip0 - 2023-07-09T163605.057.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeWwEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>These settings are available per supplier and can be enabled via the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Managing-Suppliers\">Supplier Settings</a>.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<h3 data-id=\"package-total-units\">Package Total Units</h3>\n<p>When creating a package, the total row now includes the sum of individual quantities for each component within the package.</p>\n<div><br/><div><br/><div><strong>Before:</strong><br/><img alt=\"mceclip1 - 2023-07-09T163610.858.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppdRjEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><div><strong>After:</strong><br/><img alt=\"mceclip2 (67).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppeXQEAY.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></div><br/></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<h3 data-id=\"other-improvements\">Other Improvements</h3>\n<ul><li>We've enabled <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Cash-Up-End-of-Day\">Cash Up</a> toggle in Payment Types to enable Auto-Reconciling for Gift Vouchers and Cash Rounding; <span> the amount expected will be automatically populated in the \"Amount Reconciled\" field in Step 3 of the Cash Up. </span></li></ul></div><br/></div><br/></div><br/></div>",
